And generally speaking I begin with something like the sculped draw brush which is kind of the default

02:51.940 --> 02:52.640
brush.

02:52.840 --> 03:01.210
But you've got a lot of other options here like Clay strips and blob and grab and inflate.

03:01.330 --> 03:08.680
