03:27.730 --> 03:37.170
The radius is the size of the brush and the strength is of course how strong the brush is on the object.

03:37.190 --> 03:46.330
You can also change the radius and strength of the brush by pressing the F key for radius and then click.

03:46.610 --> 03:52.820
Or you can press shift F to increase or decrease the strength.

03:52.820 --> 03:55.250
There are a lot of settings in this panel.

03:55.250 --> 04:02.870
